Maintainer: Lucas Castillo <lucas.castillo-marti@warwick.ac.uk>
Description: Understand human performance from the perspective of sampling, 
    both looking at how people generate samples and 
    how people use the samples they have generated. A longer overview and other 
    resources can be found at sampling.warwick.ac.uk.
